These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-1::.
There are 3 different nationalities: dutch, australian, british
1. the australian is on the far left##1
2. the dutch is on the right of the british##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |     2     |     3     |
| Nationality   | australian | british | dutch |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-2::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: begonia, daisy, dahlia
1. the person who growsdahlia is on the far right##1
2. the person who growsbegonia is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2    |      3       |
| Flower   | begonia | daisy | dahlia |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-3::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, dannemann, chaman
1. the bongani-smoker is on the far left##1
2. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |      3      |
| Cigar   | bongani | dannemann | chaman |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-4::.
